  "text": "Internal Sensitivity Index . Serum ALT and AST were determined enzymatically. Serum creatinine and urea were determined by standard methods. Plasma glucose and insulin analyses were performed by the glucose oxidase and double antibody radioimmunoassay methods, respectively. Plasma total lipids were analyzed by gas liquid chromatography [CITATION_1] .",
